No. 711,

Mise.

Sumrall v. United States. Lawrence A. Aschenbrenner and Elliott C. Lichtman for petitioner. Solicitor General Griswold, Assistant Attorney General Vinson, Beatrice Rosenberg, and Roger A. Pauley for the United States.

C. A. 5th Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
